'''3-羟基丁醛'''（又称丁醇醛、丁间醇醛）是一种{{link-en|羟醛|aldol}}，化学式为[[C4H8O2|C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>8</sub>O<sub>2</sub>]]，可以在[[乙醛|乙醛]]发生[[二聚体|二聚]]时生成。3-羟基丁醛在过去曾被用作[[安眠药|安眠药]]和[[镇静剂|镇静剂]]。<ref>{{Cite book | author = Hans Brandenberger, Robert A. A. Maes. | title = Analytical Toxicology: For Clinical, Forensic, and Pharmaceutical Chemists | location = New York | publisher = de Gruyter | date = 1997}}</ref>

